      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i've been doing deadlifts for a few months but lately my lower back is killing me after sets. i feel like i'm using my back more than my legs. whats going on and how do i fix my form?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey so i've been doing deadlifts for a few months but lately my lower back is killing me after sets. i feel like i'm using my back more than my legs. whats going on and how do i fix my form?",
