      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the tips. i think i've been trying to keep my spine super flat like a board, but maybe i'm being too rigid? what exactly should my spine look like during the actual pull and how do i actually \"brace\" my core properly? i feel like i'm just holding my breath.",
